LICENSE — SELECTION PENDING

Orb's license has not yet been chosen. This is a deliberate Phase 0 decision held
open for the project owner.

The choice carries architectural weight for a local-first, user-sovereign,
model-independent system and should be made explicitly. See the Phase 0 review
notes for the trade-offs under consideration (e.g. Apache-2.0 for an explicit
patent grant, AGPL-3.0 to keep network-deployed forks open, or a source-available
license).

Until a license is selected and this file is replaced, all rights are reserved by
the copyright holder.
